Original Text: \Eしまった…お茶は切らしてたんだった…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Oh no... I forgot that we ran out of tea...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]We took a break and enjoyed some green tea.

Original Text: \Eしまった…コーヒーは切らしてたんだった…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Oh no... I forgot that we ran out of coffee...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]We took a break and enjoyed some coffee.

Original Text: \E紅茶はおっと…もう無いのか…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Oh no... we don't have any more black tea...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Hmm, we don't have any of it...

Original Text: \Eそんな物は持っていないな…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I don't have it in my possession.

Original Text:
\Eそういえば試供品をもらってたな…
俺はこれにするか。
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Come to think of it, I got a free sample... 
I think I'll go with this.

Original Text: \Eこ、これは…！力がみなぎってくる…！
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Wh, what is this...! I can feel a sudden surge of power!

Original Text: \E…うーん、お茶を飲む前にすることがあったな…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...Hmm, I think I needed to do something first before having tea...

Original Text: \Eむ、無性にエナドリが飲みたい…
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I, I have an intense craving for an energy drink...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...I really want to drink it badly!
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Alright... How about I brew some tea?

Original Text: \Eまた買っておかないとだね。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]We definitely need to buy some more.

Original Text: \Eお茶くらい入れてくるよー、待っててお兄ちゃん。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I'll go and brew the tea for you, Onii-chan. Just wait here.

Original Text: \Eまた今度買ってこようね、お兄ちゃん。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Let's buy more of it next time, Onii-chan.
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]My sister is a fan of black tea...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...Wait here, I'll go brew some tea.

Original Text: \E…使っておいたほうがいいだろうな…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...It's probably better to use it just in case...

Original Text:
\E…お茶飲みたいから入れてくる。
…ジュースでいいか？
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...I feel like having some tea, so I'll go brew some. 
...Or would you rather have juice?

Original Text: \Eやった、ありがとうお兄ちゃん。
約5割の確率でトイレに
\E…ちょっとトイレ行ってくるね。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...I need to go to the toilet for a bit.
